01:35:39.735 --> 01:35:40.778
<i>What?</i>

01:35:40.986 --> 01:35:42.655
<i>I told you,
you don't belong here.</i>

01:35:42.738 --> 01:35:44.448
<i>I felt your heartbeat
when I hugged you.</i>

01:35:44.532 --> 01:35:47.076
<i>You're still alive.
